Project requirements: 

create a simple market place for bank and loan borrowers

Database Schema

    Bank Table:
        BankID (Primary Key)
        BankName
        IFSCCode

    Borrower Table:
        BorrowerID (Primary Key)
        BorrowerName
        PhoneNumber
        PANCard
        BankID (Foreign Key)

    Loan Table:
        LoanID (Primary Key)
        LoanAmount
        InterestRate
        LoanTerm
        EMIAmount
        TotalInterest
        TotalAmount
        BorrowerID (Foreign Key)

    Payment Table:
        PaymentID (Primary Key)
        PaymentDate
        PaymentAmount
        PaymentType (EMI or Lump Sum)
        LoanID (Foreign Key)
        
        
        
